metadata.description:
Holders of the ASSEMBLY 001 membership NFT are graduates of Metalabel's application-only laboratory program exploring creativity in multiplayer mode. The only way to hold this NFT is to be part of a cultural collective or creative project that completed ASSEMBLY 001. This NFT can be used to unlock future Metalabel products and services, and grants access to Metalabel's membership network in Discord.

https://assembly.metalabel.xyz
